@metadata.message-documentation: This is english locales for Web Scraper Plugin

selector-edit-clickMore: Click more (click to load more elements. Stops when no new elements with unique text content are found.)
selector-edit-discardInitialElements: Discard initial elements that are available before click
selector-edit-trim-applying: Trim will be applied before regex.
sitemap-scrape-config-alert-success:
Scraping in progress. Close the popup to stop scraping.
			When scraping is finished you can browse the data or export it as CSV.
sitemap-edit-metadata-url-patterns:
Supported URL patterns:
			1. Numeric with optional step and zero padding – [START-END:STEP] – [001-010:10]
			2. Date interval – [date<PATTERN><START><END>] – [date<dd.MM.yyyy><01.01.2017><now>]
			
				date placeholder may be
				yesterday
				/
				now
				/
				tomorrow
				other template components (in Java style)
				
					
						
							
								yyyy
								full year (4 digits)
							
							
								yy
								last 2 digits of year
							
							
								MMM  
								Jan, Feb, Mar, Apr, May, Jun, Jul, Aug, Sep, Oct, Nov, Dec
							
							
								MM
								month number (01-12)
							
							
								dd
								day of month
sitemap-edit-metadata-specify-sitemap-mo:
You can specify sitemap model as a list of json objects. 
					Example: [ { "entity": "EntityName", "field": "FieldName", "field_name": "Expected Field Id" } ]
sitemap-create-text-support-url-patterns:
Supported URL patterns:
1. Numeric with optional step and zero padding – [START-END:STEP] – [001-010:10]
2. Date interval – [date<PATTERN><START><END>] – [date<dd.MM.yyyy><01.01.2017><now>]
    date placeholder may be yesterday / now / tomorrow
    other template components (in Java style)
      yyyy full year (4 digits)
      yy last 2 digits of year
      MMM   Jan, Feb, Mar, Apr, May, Jun, Jul, Aug, Sep, Oct, Nov, Dec
      MM month number (01-12)
      dd day of month
sitemap-create-specify-sitemap-model-tex:
You can specify sitemap model as a list of json objects.
Example: [ { "entity": "EntityName", "field": "FieldName", "field_name": "Expected Field Id" } ]
popup-title: Open Developer tools where you will find Web Scraper tab
popup-any-oc: Any OS: open Tools / Developer tools
options-couchdb-database-url:
CouchDB database url. For each sitemap a new DB will be created.

sitemapid-invalid-char: Only lowercase characters (a-z), digits (0-9), or any of the characters _, $, (, ), +, -, and / are allowed. Must begin with a letter.

sitemapurl-empty-message: The start URL is required and cannot be empty

sitemapjson-empty-message: Sitemap JSON is required and cannot be empty
selectorid-underscore: Selector id cannot start with an underscore _

selector-header-empty-message: Header row selector is required and cannot be empty
selector-data-row-empty-message: Data row selector is required and cannot be empty

content-selector-different-element-selec:
Different type element selection is disabled. If the element  
			you clicked should also be included then enable this and 
			click on the element again. Usually this is not needed.
content-selector-select-child-key: Use C key to select child
content-selector-select-parent-key: Use P key to select parent
content-selector-select-element-key: Use S key to select element
content-selector-enable-key-events-title: Click here to enable key press events for selection
selector-edit-refresh-button-title: Refresh if you manually changed the selector
